<p>Jacob Conwell, I would think. However there are other authors, Doctor Cimmerian has used them twice (<a href="/rogue-ai-nveo4-yvn3e-pn6ug">'Rogue AI' (NVEO4/YVN3E/PN6UG)</a> and <a href="/scp-2987">SCP-2987</a>) also there's nothing in Zyn's post about multiple authors although that may be assumed.</p>
<p>Comparatively the SPC has ten tales, three mainlist articles, one format and two -Js by nine different authors.</p>

